Did you catch the baking demos during the @cherrybombe Holiday Baking Extravaganza? If not we've got you covered with the full demo from food stylist and recipe developer @jewelsofny! If you’d like to make your own dried fruit start two days ahead, otherwise store-bought dried fruit works great!

For the full recipe head to: https://cherrybombe.com/recipes/diana-yen-matcha-wreath-cake
